    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_197058">Actually all classes can start the Combat wheel (or Heroic Opportunity) -- it's just that you had to do the first one blind.  After the first time, the cursors will flash indicating what needs to be hit next to activate the Heroic Opportunity.  The Scout Archetype is the only one who can help decide what way the wheel goes (everyone else is random).   It's a nice tool for soloing; but if a group can have the patience the group ones are also very powerful -- it's just combat is so fast very few people bother with it when in groups.<br />
<br />
Don't get too reliant on soloing though would be my main advice though.  After all, it's a MMORPG and as a group ou can take on a LOT more and a lot faster.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
