    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_197127">Hmm, the way to best clarify that the scout HO is controllable to a degree is that when in a group and the scout starts an HO the others in the group can choose which way to take the wheel.   With all other classes there is no second possibility when a HO is started.  So, while in a solo role it's still useful; the scout really shines in a group.</div>
