    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_198281">Got this to rock for me solo'n at lvl 11 in Commons, and I have extremely lousy gear on hounds, and Orc Ghosts.<br />
<br />
If possible sneak and ambush, otherwise I would just pull with snare.  Then hit lucky break and my first combo would be Dirty Tricks, Then Quick Strike, this would get you a rocking ringing blow.  Wait a few secons, trigger HO again, then turn off attack, hit cheap shot, strafe around and Backstab.  <br />
<br />
Sometimes I would get a chain going, and get swindlers luck.  <br />
<br />
I haven't completely figured out my combo's, but it was working good.<br />
<br />
Can't wait to get some upgrades to my BS, quick strike, etc.<br />
<br />
I am just so poor :(<br />
<br />
Wish someo pimp quests for Freeport area would get posted.</div>
