    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_198306">Ok got it figured out for solo.<br />
<br />
You tigger HO, then you do one of the flashing skills to trigger either swindlers luck or ringing blow.  Swindlers luck is a attack buff that last 3 minutes, and ringing blow rocks for damage.<br />
<br />
If you trigger an event you don't like, say swindlers luck JUST after you just got the buff you have a chance to switch it to the other by doing a scout skill that isn't flashing.  It may or may not change, but it is good to try if you want or need to do big damage instead.<br />
<br />
Another Rare one is Bravo's Dance which is a NICE haste buff.  I am making silver quickly this way wuwu, finally get some upgrades soon.<br />
<br />
In a group, you are cool cause you can change it to something that may be more desirable, this is something that will take lots of pracitice.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
