    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_198387">I'm soloing yellow Mobs at level 13 and at times only losing one bulb of health.  Make sure you understand HO and how to flip it to ringing blow.   Also, make your you use poisons as they really increase your damage.  Buy them at a merchant and put them in your activatable slot.  Each charge last hours so you don't need to buy much.  As you level, make sure you upgrade to more powerful poisons.<br />
<br />
<br />
Orlun, Najena</div>
