    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_204005">Typical battle for me:<br />
<br />
Sneak<br />
Backstab<br />
Lucky Strike<br />
Dirty Trick<br />
Evade (if I don't like the HO that came up)<br />
Quick Strike<br />
Cheap Shot<br />
Auto Attack Off<br />
Backstab/Sneak Attack (whichever comes up)<br />
<br />
rinse, repeat. Soloing is a lot easier.<br />
<br />
Are there any other HO's asides from <br />
Lucky Strike/Dirty Tricks/Quick Strike?<br />
<br />
That rogues can do solo, I mean.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
