    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_204080">There are three different HOs that scouts can trigger that way (later quick strike can be replace by higher leveled attacks).<br />
<br />
That remains the only way to trigger a solo HO though.  Basically, if any class triggers an HO and then starts it (Lucky Strike -&gt; Dirty Tricks) it starts their own solo HO.  In groups, a different class has to move it along after you start it to get a different effect.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
